  <scopecontent id="aspace_d5b96ee8eb006d06cecb5eff79e49f2f">
    <head>Scope and Contents</head>
<p>The bulk of this collection consists of materials related to Baer's telecasted educational program on WCBS-TV called "Our Goodly Heritage." To a lesser extent, the collection contains materials Baer created and gathered while working at New York University. Collection materials include correspondence, press releases, news clippings, and typescripts. Materials date from 1944 to 1958.</p>  </scopecontent>
